Introduction

Seyoung is a South Korean singer and actor. He formerly served as the main vocalist of the boy group CROSS GENE. He joined the group in January 2013, following J.G's departure to pursue a solo career, and left in November 2020.

On January 29, 2019, he debuted as a soloist with the release of the single "Winter Rain."

On October 16, 2021, he released the single "Loop", his first release under his new stage name COiBLEN.

He acted in the movie ZEDD (2014) alongside the other Cross Gene group members.

He played the Brave Gold Dino in Power Rangers Dino Force Brave in 2017.
